\sum_{k=1}^n \frac{k}{(k+1)!} = \frac{(n+1)!-1}{(n+1)!}
\sum_{k=1}^n \frac{k}{(k+1)!} =\sum_{k=1}^n \frac{k+1-1}{(k+1)!}=\sum_{k=1}^n \frac{1}{k!}- \frac{1}{(k+1)!}=1-\frac{1}{(n+1)!}
